        "subject": "LU-0000 test: Run Ubuntu full test session",
        "message": "LU-0000 test: Run Ubuntu full test session\n\nThe Debian build is broken and we cannot run Ubuntu testing\nin autotest. The patch for LU-10569 with commit 1a6518a70758d\nis supposed to fix this issue.\n\nRun the full test session with Ubuntu clients to test if\nwe can build and run testing and validate the LU-10569 patch.\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly clientdistro=ubuntu1604 clientbuildno=55443 clientcount=2 serverdistro=el7 serverbuildno=55443 mdscount=1 mdtcount=1 osscount=1 ostcount=7 envdefinitions=SLOW=yes,ENABLE_QUOTA=yes testgroup=full\nSigned-off-by: James Nunez <james.a.nunez@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I8d67363f7cc4d69592d25fa677c4bf9c26fba0ac\n"
      },
